These are just notes:

Common resolutions for 16:9 are listed in the table below:
Width Height Standard
256   144    
320   180    QnHD
426   240    NTSC widescreen
640   360    nHD
848   480    
854   480    FWVGA
960   540    qHD
1024  576    
1280  720    HD
1366  768    
1600  900    HD+
1920  1080   Full HD
2560  1440   QHD
3200  1800   QHD+
3840  2160   4K UHD
5120  2880   5K
7680  4320   8K UHD

ffmpeg -r <framerate> -f image2 -s <width>x<height> -i %04d.png -vcodec h264_nvenc -crf 25 -pix_fmt yuv420p output.mp4

